{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "Garasi Log API",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "Vehicle maintenance record API. All endpoints require `Authorization: Bearer <API_TOKEN>`.\n\n## Conventions\n\n- Money: full rupiah, integer (`108000`, never `108` or `108.000`)\n- Dates: ISO `yyyy-mm-dd` strings\n- `category` is required on every item: `rutin` | `aksesoris` | `administratif`\n- No silent defaults: missing required fields return `400 {\"error\": \"missing field: <name>\"}`. Exception: `total` is computed as `round(unit_price × qty)` when omitted\n- `due_km` is an **absolute odometer value**, not an interval: \"next oil change in 3000 km\" at odometer 32000 → `due_km: 35000`\n\n## Receipt entry workflow\n\nWhen entering a workshop receipt (photo or text):\n\n1. `GET /api/vehicles` to resolve the vehicle id; ask if the receipt doesn't clearly match one vehicle\n2. Decide where the items go:\n   - routine service visit → new session: `POST /api/vehicles/{id}/sessions` with `date`, `odometer_km`, `items`. Ask for the odometer reading if the receipt doesn't show it\n   - follow-up work belonging to a recent visit → append: `POST /api/sessions/{id}/items`\n   - accessories or administrative costs (pajak, STNK, balik nama) → sessionless: `POST /api/vehicles/{id}/items`\n3. Normalize prices to full-rupiah integers (\"60rb\" → 60000, \"1,2jt\" → 1200000)\n4. If a next-service interval is mentioned, set `due_date` and/or `due_km` (absolute odometer) on that item\n5. Confirm the parsed items with the user before posting\n\nA checkpoint becomes *due* when `due_date` is within `REMINDER_DAYS_AHEAD` (14) days, or `due_km` is within `REMINDER_KM_AHEAD` (500) km of the vehicle's current odometer (max over maintenance sessions and the odometer/fuel log). Sold vehicles are excluded. Due checkpoints are sent daily at 05:00 WIB via Telegram.\n\n## Refuel entry workflow\n\nWhen given odometer + fuel receipt photos: read the odometer km from the dashboard photo and date/liters/total from the receipt, then `POST /api/vehicles/{id}/odometer`. Full-tank refuels make km/l accurate; log a plain odometer reading (no liters/total) anytime to keep reminders fresh.",
    "license": { "name": "MIT", "url": "https://github.com/endymuhardin/vehicle-maintenance/blob/main/LICENSE" }
  },
  "externalDocs": {
    "description": "Source and full documentation",
    "url": "https://github.com/endymuhardin/vehicle-maintenance"
  },
  "servers": [{ "url": "/" }],
  "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
  "tags": [
    { "name": "vehicles" },
    { "name": "sessions" },
    { "name": "checkpoints" },
    { "name": "fuel" }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/api/vehicles": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["vehicles"],
        "summary": "List vehicles with summary stats",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "All vehicles, including sold ones",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VehicleSummary" } },
                "example": [
                  { "id": 1, "name": "Corolla Twincam", "status": "active", "latest_km": 180000, "session_count": 5, "spend": 58646000 },
                  { "id": 2, "name": "Revo Fit 2012", "status": "sold", "latest_km": 56000, "session_count": 1, "spend": 3654475 }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" }
        }
      },
      "post": {
        "tags": ["vehicles"],
        "summary": "Create a vehicle",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name"],
                "properties": { "name": { "type": "string" } }
              },
              "example": { "name": "Yamaha NMAX 2026" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Created (status is always `active`)",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 5, "name": "Yamaha NMAX 2026", "status": "active" } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/vehicles/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["vehicles"],
        "summary": "Vehicle detail with its maintenance sessions",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Vehicle with sessions ordered by seq",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VehicleDetail" },
                "example": {
                  "id": 4, "name": "Yamaha All New Vixion 2017", "status": "active",
                  "latest_km": 32000, "last_date": "2026-06-01", "session_count": 1, "spend": 190000,
                  "sessions": [
                    { "id": 8, "seq": 1, "date": "2026-06-01", "odometer_km": 32000, "item_count": 3, "total": 190000 }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/vehicles/{id}/sessions": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["sessions"],
        "summary": "Create a maintenance session with line items (receipt entry)",
        "description": "The primary endpoint for entering a workshop receipt. Creates the session (\"Perawatan ke-N\", `seq` auto-incremented per vehicle) and its line items in one call. `items` is required but may be empty.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["date", "odometer_km", "items"],
                "properties": {
                  "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
                  "odometer_km": { "type": "integer" },
                  "items": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ItemInput" } }
                }
              },
              "example": {
                "date": "2026-06-01",
                "odometer_km": 32000,
                "items": [
                  { "description": "Oli mesin Yamalube", "unit_price": 60000, "qty": 1, "category": "rutin", "date": "2026-06-01", "due_km": 35000, "checkpoint_note": "tiap 3000 km" },
                  { "description": "Jasa servis ringan", "unit_price": 85000, "qty": 1, "category": "rutin", "date": "2026-06-01" }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Session created with items",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 8, "vehicle_id": 4, "seq": 1, "date": "2026-06-01", "odometer_km": 32000, "item_count": 2 } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/vehicles/{id}/items": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["vehicles"],
        "summary": "Add sessionless expenses (aksesoris / administratif)",
        "description": "For costs not tied to a maintenance session: accessories, pajak, STNK, balik nama.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["items"],
                "properties": {
                  "items": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ItemInput" } }
                }
              },
              "example": { "items": [{ "description": "Pajak tahunan", "unit_price": 280000, "qty": 1, "category": "administratif", "date": "2026-05-20" }] }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Items inserted",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "vehicle_id": 4, "inserted": 1 } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/sessions/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["sessions"],
        "summary": "Session detail with line items",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Session with full line_items rows",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SessionDetail" } } }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/sessions/{id}/items": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["sessions"],
        "summary": "Append line items to an existing session",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["items"],
                "properties": {
                  "items": { "type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ItemInput" } }
                }
              },
              "example": { "items": [{ "description": "Kampas rem belakang", "unit_price": 45000, "qty": 1, "category": "rutin", "date": "2026-06-01" }] }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Items inserted",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "session_id": 8, "inserted": 1 } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/vehicles/{id}/odometer": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["fuel"],
        "summary": "Odometer / fuel log with km/l calculations",
        "description": "Entries newest first. `km_per_liter` is computed per fuel entry against the previous fuel entry (full-tank method). `avg_km_per_liter` spans first to last fill.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Fuel log summary",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/FuelSummary" },
                "example": {
                  "entries": [
                    { "id": 2, "vehicle_id": 3, "date": "2026-05-20", "odometer_km": 61550, "liters": 3.2, "total": 43200, "note": "Pertalite", "km_per_liter": 46.88 },
                    { "id": 1, "vehicle_id": 3, "date": "2026-05-01", "odometer_km": 61400, "liters": 3.5, "total": 47250, "note": "Pertalite", "km_per_liter": null }
                  ],
                  "avg_km_per_liter": 46.88,
                  "total_fuel_cost": 90450,
                  "total_liters": 6.7
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      },
      "post": {
        "tags": ["fuel"],
        "summary": "Log an odometer reading, optionally with refuel data",
        "description": "With `liters` + `total`: a refuel entry (full tank assumed for km/l accuracy). Without both: a plain odometer reading. Providing only one of the two is a 400. Odometer readings feed the reminder engine: a vehicle's current km = max over sessions and this log.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["date", "odometer_km"],
                "properties": {
                  "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
                  "odometer_km": { "type": "integer" },
                  "liters": { "type": "number" },
                  "total": { "type": "integer", "description": "Rupiah paid" },
                  "note": { "type": "string", "description": "e.g. station, fuel type" }
                }
              },
              "example": { "date": "2026-06-04", "odometer_km": 48210, "liters": 8.5, "total": 110500, "note": "Pertamax, Shell Cibinong" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Created entry with computed km/l",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 3, "vehicle_id": 4, "date": "2026-06-04", "odometer_km": 48210, "liters": 8.5, "total": 110500, "note": "Pertamax", "km_per_liter": 44.1, "avg_km_per_liter": 45.2 } } }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/items/{id}/done": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["checkpoints"],
        "summary": "Mark a checkpoint as handled",
        "description": "Removes the item from reminder digests.",
        "parameters": [{ "$ref": "#/components/parameters/Id" }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Checkpoint marked done",
            "content": { "application/json": { "example": { "id": 195, "checkpoint_done": 1 } } }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "404": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/NotFound" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/due": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["checkpoints"],
        "summary": "Currently due checkpoints",
        "description": "What the daily Telegram cron would send. `overdue: true` when the date has passed or the odometer has reached `due_km`; otherwise upcoming within the reminder window.",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Due checkpoints on active vehicles",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DueItem" } },
                "example": [
                  { "id": 195, "description": "Oli Mesin", "due_date": "2026-04-01", "due_km": null, "vehicle_id": 3, "vehicle_name": "Mio Smile 2010", "latest_km": 61154, "overdue": true }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "bearerAuth": { "type": "http", "scheme": "bearer" }
    },
    "parameters": {
      "Id": {
        "name": "id",
        "in": "path",
        "required": true,
        "schema": { "type": "integer" }
      }
    },
    "responses": {
      "BadRequest": {
        "description": "Validation error",
        "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error" }, "example": { "error": "missing field: category" } } }
      },
      "Unauthorized": {
        "description": "Invalid or missing API token",
        "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error" }, "example": { "error": "invalid or missing API token" } } }
      },
      "NotFound": {
        "description": "Resource not found",
        "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error" }, "example": { "error": "vehicle 99 not found" } } }
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "Error": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": { "error": { "type": "string" } }
      },
      "VehicleSummary": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "name": { "type": "string" },
          "status": { "type": "string", "enum": ["active", "sold"] },
          "latest_km": { "type": ["integer", "null"], "description": "Highest session odometer, null if no sessions" },
          "session_count": { "type": "integer" },
          "spend": { "type": "integer", "description": "Sum of all line item totals, rupiah" }
        }
      },
      "VehicleDetail": {
        "allOf": [
          { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/VehicleSummary" },
          {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "last_date": { "type": ["string", "null"], "format": "date" },
              "sessions": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SessionSummary" } }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "SessionSummary": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "seq": { "type": "integer", "description": "Perawatan ke-N, per vehicle" },
          "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
          "odometer_km": { "type": "integer" },
          "item_count": { "type": "integer" },
          "total": { "type": "integer" }
        }
      },
      "SessionDetail": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "vehicle_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "seq": { "type": "integer" },
          "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
          "odometer_km": { "type": "integer" },
          "items": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LineItem" } }
        }
      },
      "ItemInput": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["description", "unit_price", "qty", "category"],
        "properties": {
          "description": { "type": "string" },
          "unit_price": { "type": "integer", "description": "Full rupiah" },
          "qty": { "type": "number" },
          "total": { "type": "integer", "description": "Defaults to round(unit_price × qty)" },
          "category": { "type": "string", "enum": ["rutin", "aksesoris", "administratif"] },
          "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
          "checkpoint_note": { "type": "string", "description": "Free-text service note" },
          "due_date": { "type": "string", "format": "date", "description": "Reminder by date" },
          "due_km": { "type": "integer", "description": "Reminder by ABSOLUTE odometer km, not interval" }
        }
      },
      "LineItem": {
        "allOf": [
          { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ItemInput" },
          {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "id": { "type": "integer" },
              "vehicle_id": { "type": "integer" },
              "session_id": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
              "checkpoint_done": { "type": "integer", "enum": [0, 1] }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "FuelEntry": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "vehicle_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "date": { "type": "string", "format": "date" },
          "odometer_km": { "type": "integer" },
          "liters": { "type": ["number", "null"] },
          "total": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
          "note": { "type": ["string", "null"] },
          "km_per_liter": { "type": ["number", "null"], "description": "vs previous fuel entry; null for first fill or plain readings" }
        }
      },
      "FuelSummary": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "entries": { "type": "array", "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/FuelEntry" } },
          "avg_km_per_liter": { "type": ["number", "null"] },
          "total_fuel_cost": { "type": "integer" },
          "total_liters": { "type": "number" }
        }
      },
      "DueItem": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": { "type": "integer" },
          "description": { "type": "string" },
          "vehicle_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "vehicle_name": { "type": "string" },
          "due_date": { "type": ["string", "null"], "format": "date" },
          "due_km": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
          "latest_km": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
          "overdue": { "type": "boolean" }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
